resources.description:
Creates a new user in the database with the specified credentials.

<!-- RESPONSE 200 -->
{
  "data": {
    "type": "user",
    "attributes": {
      "email": "user@kulturdaten.berlin",
      "created_at": "2021-04-27T12:26:26.130+02:00",
      "updated_at": "2021-04-27T12:26:26.147+02:00",
      "id": 1
    }
  },
  "meta": {
    "message": "Account created successfully"
  }
}

<!-- ENDRESPONSE -->

<!-- RESPONSE 422 -->
{
  "errors": [
    {
      "rule": "required",
      "field": "email",
      "message": "required validation failed"
    },
    {
      "rule": "unique",
      "field": "email",
      "message": "unique validation failure"
    },
    {
      "rule": "required",
      "field": "password",
      "message": "required validation failed"
    },
    {
      "rule": "confirmed",
      "field": "password_confirmation",
      "message": "confirmed validation failed"
    }
  ]
}

<!-- ENDRESPONSE -->

Used to verify the email address of a user. This endpoint is not meant to be called from a service but valid URLs will only be issued by the system itself.

<!-- RESPONSE 200 -->
{
  "data": null,
  "meta": {
    "message": "Successfully verified account"
  }
}

<!-- ENDRESPONSE -->

<!-- RESPONSE 400 -->
{
  "errors": [
    {
      "title": "E_UNAUTHORIZED: The embedded route signature is invalid",
      "code": "E_UNAUTHORIZED",
      "status": 400
    }
  ]
}

<!-- ENDRESPONSE -->

<!-- RESPONSE 409 -->
{
  "errors": [
    {
      "title": "E_USER_ALREADY_VERIFIED: This user's email address has already been verified",
      "code": "E_USER_ALREADY_VERIFIED",
      "status": 409
    }
  ]
}

<!-- ENDRESPONSE -->

Logs a user into the appplication and returns an API token to authenticate on other routes.

<!-- RESPONSE 200 -->
{
  "meta": {
    "token": {
      "type": "bearer",
      "token": "Mg.6D5gnL1arE8DfUeN0KfGY3Ks1FniZ8oH4RX55L9qywsQHfEblSp4tCog84Mg"
    },
    "message": "Logged in successfully",
    "language": "de"
  }
}

<!-- ENDRESPONSE -->

<!-- RESPONSE 422 -->
{
  "errors": [
    {
      "rule": "required",
      "field": "email",
      "message": "required validation failed"
    },
    {
      "rule": "required",
      "field": "password",
      "message": "required validation failed"
    }
  ]
}
<!-- ENDRESPONSE -->

Returns information about the user currently logged in.

<!-- RESPONSE 200 -->
{
  "data": {
    "id": 1,
    "type": "user",
    "attributes": {
      "email": "user@kulturdaten.berlin",
      "rememberMeToken": null,
      "status": "active",
      "createdAt": "2021-06-03T16:25:51.000+02:00",
      "updatedAt": "2021-06-03T16:25:51.000+02:00"
    }
  },
  "meta": {
    "language": "de"
  }
}

<!-- ENDRESPONSE -->

<!-- RESPONSE 401 -->
{
  "errors": [
    {
      "title": "E_UNAUTHORIZED: The action you try to perform is only allowed for authenticated users.",
      "code": "E_UNAUTHORIZED",
      "status": 401
    }
  ]
}

<!-- ENDRESPONSE -->

Checks if the header user for authorization is still valid.

<!-- RESPONSE 200 -->
{
  "meta": {
    "valid": true,
    "language": "de"
  }
}

<!-- ENDRESPONSE -->

<!-- RESPONSE 200 -->
{
  "meta": {
    "valid": false,
    "language": "de"
  }
}

<!-- ENDRESPONSE -->

Logs a user out of the application. Does never fail.

<!-- RESPONSE 200 -->
{
  "meta": {
    "message": "Logged out successfully",
    "language": "de"
  }
}

